<DOCOLDNO>IA078-000523-B043-255</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.mcwilliams.com:80/books/aint/215.htm 207.171.3.168 19970124130316 text/html 15324
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 13:02:17 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
