<a href="http://www.mcwilliams.com"><IMG BORDER=1 width=50 height=18 SRC="../../images/home.gif" ALT="HOME"></A>
</h4>

<IMG SRC="../../images/line1.gif">
<P>
<B>Copyright &copy; 1996 <A HREF="mailto:peter@mcwilliams.com">Peter McWilliams</A> & Prelude Press</B>
<p>
Last Revision:  December 2, 1996</FONT>
<p>
<IMG SRC="../../images/green.gif" width=300 height=4>
<p>
</P></DIV></CENTER>
</BODY>
</HTML>

</DOC>
