<DOCOLDNO>IA078-000523-B045-343</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.mcwilliams.com:80/books/aint/503.htm 207.171.3.168 19970124131129 text/html 15462
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 13:10:28 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
