<PRE>

</PRE><FONT SIZE=7>HOW TO HEAL DEPRESSION</FONT>
<p>
<HR width=75% size=2 align=left noshade><p>
<p>
<center><IMG SRC="../../images/line1.gif">
<p>
<H2>TABLE OF CONTENTS </H2>


<H3><A HREF="depintr.htm">Introduction</A></H3>
</center>
<p>
<DL COMPACT>
<p>
<DT><H3>PART I: <A HREF="dep1a.htm">Understanding Depression</A> </H3>
<p>
<DD><A HREF="dep1a.htm #One">One</A>: You Are Not Alone
<DD><A HREF="dep1a.htm #Two">Two</A>: If You Need It, Get Help at Once
<DD><A HREF="dep1a.htm #Three">Three</A>: There Is No Need to Suffer
<DD><A HREF="dep1a.htm #Four">Four</A>: "I Can't Handle Anything Else!"
